# RENVO Icon Vector 1
#
# Fixed 16x16 view box. Commands:
#   I name                         begin an icon
#   L x1 y1 x2 y2 width            line
#   R x y width height stroke      outlined rectangle
#   F x y width height             filled rectangle
#   O x y width height stroke      outlined ellipse
#   E x y width height             filled ellipse
#   P stroke count x1 y1 ...       polyline
#   G count x1 y1 ...              filled convex polygon
# Prefix a drawing command with A to use the icon's accent color.

I new
